  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/62c65f75422900f161838a83f2b2b6c0.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d4361f8d134d00a66c48fb9ca5dd4a02.poster.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d4361f8d134d00a66c48fb9ca5dd4a02.webm?t=1749385638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d9c8548b6b17979322adfde9046758c2.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a man captured by demons and forced to do manual labor. After some time, you can take no more and try to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that's easier said than done!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid roaming patrols, hidden traps, and devious illusions in a mad dash for freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Dungeon Escape Action Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak Past Patrolling Demons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid A Variety of Traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the Labyrinth and Escape!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/62c65f75422900f161838a83f2b2b6c0.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d4361f8d134d00a66c48fb9ca5dd4a02.poster.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d4361f8d134d00a66c48fb9ca5dd4a02.webm?t=1749385638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455220/extras/d9c8548b6b17979322adfde9046758c2.avif?t=1749385638\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a man captured by demons and forced to do manual labor. After some time, you can take no more and try to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that's easier said than done!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid roaming patrols, hidden traps, and devious illusions in a mad dash for freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Dungeon Escape Action Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak Past Patrolling Demons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid A Variety of Traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the Labyrinth and Escape!</p></li></ul>",
